{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_9", "eventName": "風暴瞭望", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "9-10", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "雷聲轟鳴", "storyInfo": "號角被上校的人控制。Outcast正與羅德島幹員部署撤退事宜，聽到上空傳來異響。風笛找到信使，可就在這時，駐軍對城區的大轟炸開始了。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G3_victoria_street_d"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然來了，就都出來吧。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#2"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_248", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "中尉。", "name": "副官希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的人怎麼樣了？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_248"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的屬下在這裡。放心，他們只是暈了過去。", "name": "副官希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說的不是大提琴他們。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我指的是誰。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_248"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "副官希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$sheildimpact"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別逼我，否則的話，抵著你下巴的就不是我的盾了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳、咳咳......要是您拔劍的話，您就是在襲擊同僚......", "name": "副官希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，同僚？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從我們進入小丘郡的那一刻起，你們何曾把我們當成同僚？！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "回答我！！！", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶——", "name": "副官希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算......您......在這裡切斷我的喉管......您也不能改變......上校的決定......", "name": "副官希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 47, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_248", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是嗎？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的沒有聽說過風暴突擊隊的戰士能做到什麼程度，是不是？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三角鐵讓你們損失了多少人？半支連隊？", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡只有我一個。但是，我向你保證，你不會想知道我搞定你們需要花多少時間。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你、你放下武器！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不然的話，我......我們這就殺了她！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_241", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......大提琴。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#4"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_241", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說真的！你敢動一下，我的弩立刻射穿她的脖子！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_241"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_241", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "............", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#7"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_241", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們贏了。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$sheildimpact"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_241"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "exit", "direction": "right", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "制服她！快上，一起上，不能讓她再碰到盾和劍！", "name": "維多利亞士兵"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "希爾......你告訴漢密爾頓......", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "維多利亞以他為恥。", "name": "號角"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_229_1#1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_248"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......上校並不需要維多利亞的感激。", "name": "副官希爾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_248"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G9_rhodes_xqoffice", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.8, "crossfade": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "資料都整理好了嗎？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的，女士，都在這裡了。", "name": "幹員弗雷德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_012"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_012", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很好。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧利弗，我注意到你也發完電訊了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "合作企業都收到了通知。根據協定條款，之後他們會去找附近其他城市的辦事處，或者終止合約。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，這麼看，我們的損失還不小啊。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#2", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在戰亂中蒙受損失的企業不止羅德島。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#2", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是，沒辦法，就是我看著這些桌子椅子實在心裡難受。當年我剛來小丘郡的時候，我們這間屋子還是空的。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧利弗，陷在離別之愁裡還為時過早，你又怎麼知道我們不會馬上回來呢？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您說的沒錯。唉，希望很快這座城市又能恢復往日的平靜。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......倉庫裡的藥，清點結束。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩你們把這些藥分一分，確保每個人都能帶上足量的應急藥品，直到大家順利轉移至最近的辦事處。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣分完，還剩下很多。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "全帶走的話會有些壓力，畢竟我們人沒那麼多。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_089", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "碎紙機，雖然你沉默依舊，但我看得出來，你有自己的想法。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#3"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_089", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......城裡的人們，需要藥品。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_089", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛好，我也這麼認為。一旦戰火蔓延開，各項基礎補給都會告急，尤其是需要長期服用的礦石病鎮痛和抑制藥物。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想你應該有附近醫院的名單吧？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_089", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......已經整理好了。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_089", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "想辦法給他們送過去。無論這些機構為誰服務，都要儘量送到。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，別忘記那些開在巷子裡的小診所，它們大多沒有招牌，可我們相當多的當地朋友們全指望它們。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，這樣真的妥當嗎？我們一般並不直接越過當地藥企，給醫療機構和個人提供藥品。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常時期，非常舉措。更何況，不會有多少醫院拒絕來自熱心市民的“匿名捐贈”吧？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "確實！原來您都想好了啊。可是我們誰負責去送呢？附近的人們都知道我們是羅德島的人。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我去。我會幫助碎紙機大哥打包藥品，然後我來送藥。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#6$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡，你好些了？", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傷口不再流血了。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道我問的不是傷口。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大家都在忙碌的時候，我不想一個人躲在一旁哭泣。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有你幫忙當然是好事，不過，藥可不少。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請相信瓦伊凡的體能。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是不希望羅德島的任務耽誤你自己的計畫。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事的。從這裡到交戰區，剛好能路過好幾家醫院和診所。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等送完藥，我就會歸隊。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#8$1"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還差一點，很快打包就能完成。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那大家也差不多該上路了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Outcast說著，從身側的武器袋中拔出了一把左輪手銃。"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，這就是您的銃嗎？", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對薩科塔來說，行動之前，總要填好子彈才算準備萬全。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您的彈倉好像沒滿。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "通常情況下，同時射出五發子彈也夠用了。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在回本艦和巴蒂他們吃飯的時候，聽過很多您的外勤故事。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您曾經用一發子彈幹掉過三個哥倫比亞匪首，用三發子彈打散過一支雇傭兵隊伍。", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要我說，沒什麼敵人值得您連開六槍吧？", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "name2": "char_013_riop", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那可未必。畢竟，更大的挑戰永遠在前方。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我答應過一個人，我不會輕易射出六發子彈——因為我們打了一個賭。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我忍不住好奇，什麼樣的賭約會讓您這樣的人改變行事方法？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "解釋起來會有那麼一點複雜。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，我的那位朋友想方設法地要讓我舒舒服服地享受退休生活。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#2"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我總是有一種預感，像我這樣的人，即便哪一天真的退休了，也沒法過得太平靜。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像現在這樣嗎？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也沒想到小丘郡會變得這麼不平靜，明明幾十個小時前，我們還聚在一起打牌喝茶......", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#5$1"}, {"id": 200, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "許多時候，局勢就如同天色，總是瞬息萬變。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#6"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1", "name2": "avg_npc_245_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能選擇的話，我還是希望這次撤退行動能平靜些，最好連一顆子彈都用不上。", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......女士，都準備好了。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "朋友們，是時候說再見了。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小簡妮......", "name": "幹員奧利弗"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不必這麼難過，奧利弗叔叔，我相信Outcast的話——我們一定還能再見面的！", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#7$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_089"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "簡，小心。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_089"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我會的，碎紙機大哥。你們也是，務必保全自己。", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......我是不是聽見了雷聲？", "name": "簡妮"}, "figure_art": "avg_479_sleach_1#4$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_013_riop"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......馬上就要下雨了。", "name": "幹員碎紙機"}, "figure_art": "char_013_riop"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這個聲音不大對勁。簡，你先別出門！", "name": "Outcast"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_245_1#5"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$tense_intro", "key": "$tense_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廚子先生，廚子先生你在嗎？！", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "fadetime": 1.5, "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎喲，我在，我在的！別拍門啦，我們這辦公室的門被油煙燻久了，可不經敲。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "fadetime": 1.5, "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您還在就好......是這樣的，我要找信使，我們有重要的消息要傳出城去！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我都明白。剛好，我也有東西要交給你。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？這是什麼？一張......紙？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是一名駐軍軍官——叫路易士·凱利的那位，他剛剛交給我的。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "凱利上尉？他怎麼會跟你聯絡？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，他壓根不知道我是誰，只不過因為我是他最後撞見的人。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我本來是去周圍打探消息，畢竟我記得自己的老本行是吧......沒想到我竟然遇上了駐軍在抓他！", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 267, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抓......他？你的意思是，凱利上尉被自己人抓了？！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們說他窩藏礦石病人！可這不對啊，他兒子幾個月前因為礦石病去世，城裡的人都知道，他第一時間就上報了他兒子生病的消息！", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 271, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這群人......拿這麼悲慘的疾病當藉口？太無恥了吧！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 273, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不是一次兩次了，對想把各種歧視擺上檯面的人來說，礦石病真是一個特別好用的幌子。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像這次，駐軍是為了清理內部塔拉出身的人。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是軍官還是士兵，只要家裡和塔拉人沾親帶故，都在一夜之間被剝奪了自由行動的權利。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 277, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "清理軍隊內部的塔拉人？在急需用人的戰時？我有一些很不好的預感。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 279, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，凱利上尉拼命塞給我這張紙，想讓我交給“最近一直在附近晃悠的不是駐軍的士兵”——", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廚子先生，這是駐軍在製造非法源石武器的證據！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？！漢密爾頓是瘋了吧！", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請你找到可信的信使，把這張紙和我們關於鬼魂部隊的報告放在一起，作為重要情報，立刻帶出小丘郡！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是上尉在最後關頭的努力，我們一定不能白費！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 289, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不行，這些消息太重要了，民間信使並不牢靠。這樣吧，女士，我自己跑這趟。", "name": "廚子麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 291, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "廚子先生，您也當過信使嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別忘了，傳遞消息也是我們點燈人老本行的一部分。哎，我這總算能接點像樣的任務了，我的手跟腿都在興奮地發抖。", "name": "信使麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦等下，外面有什麼聲音......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是在打雷吧？", "name": "信使麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我覺得不太像。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，我在小丘郡待了這麼多年，這天氣說變就變，我都習慣了。", "name": "信使麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "avg_npc_242", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這點雷雨還攔不住我，我走了！", "name": "信使麥克馬丁"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G3_victoria_street_d"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.25, "g": 0.25, "b": 0.25, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainheavy_loop", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "信使頭也不回地衝向街道深處。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在他頭頂，大雨傾盆而下，雷聲漸漸近了，越來越密集，越來越響——", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.25, "g": 0.25, "b": 0.25, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這......這不是打雷！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，廚子先生——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#6"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——這是炮轟聲！！！", "name": "風笛"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rainheavy_loop", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 0.4, "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "21_G3_victoria_street_d"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.25, "g": 0.25, "b": 0.25, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "信使沒來得及聽見她的話。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "無數炮彈乘著大雨降下，在接觸到地面和牆體的一瞬炸裂開來。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "衝擊波輕鬆撕開了凝膠材料，高溫兇猛地熔化了金屬結構，而更可怕的是趁機鑽入城市肌骨之下的病原——", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "不完全燃燒形成巨大的源石晶簇，密集地凝結在街道和建築的傷口裡，就如同一朵朵在泥雨中迅速盛開的純黑花朵。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 0.25, "g": 0.25, "b": 0.25, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}